projects.name: Brain Tumor Detection Research Paper
projects.description: Utilizing object detection techniques in Matlab and Python for automated identification and analysis of brain tumors within medical imaging. Introduced a novel convolution-based hybrid model to improve brain tumor identification accuracy, comparing deep learning algorithms such as Inception V3, GoogleNet, and Vgg-19. Explored fusion techniques and transfer learning to enhance model performance, achieving significant improvements in accuracy and robustness.

projects.name: Loan Prediction System
projects.description: Performed exploratory Data analysis on the dataset provided to us. Achieved accurate results by cleaning the dataset and utilizing decision tree algorithms for output generation.

projects.name: AdventureWorks Business Intelligence Dashboard
projects.description: Developed dynamic PowerBI dashboard showcasing sales, inventory, and customer data with interactive visualizations and drill-down capabilities. Efficiently extracted and transformed data using Power Query, establishing accurate data models for sales and inventory analysis. Overcame challenges by optimizing SQL queries and implementing user-driven design improvements, empowering stakeholders with actionable insights for strategic decision-making.
